Nagawa ko yun dahil sa traffic.

00:27:40.940 --> 00:27:41.860
Tingnan mo, Lola?

00:27:42.340 --> 00:27:43.820
Hindi talaga ako nagsisinungaling.

00:27:46.300 --> 00:27:48.420
Xiaofei, palagi kang ganyan

00:27:48.540 --> 00:27:50.420
sobrang pabaya.

00:27:50.420 --> 00:27:51.420
Hiniram mo ang kotse para masaya

00:27:51.420 --> 00:27:52.820
at naging sanhi ng hindi pagkakaunawaan!

